result:
<v-form
  ref="form"
  v-model="valid"
  lazy-validation
>
  <v-text-field
    v-model="name"
    :counter="10"
    :rules="nameRules"
    label="Name"
    required
  ></v-text-field>

  <v-text-field
    v-model="email"
    :rules="emailRules"
    label="E-mail"
    required
  ></v-text-field>

  <v-checkbox
    v-model="legislacaocheckbox"
    :rules="[v => !!v || 'You must agree to continue!']"
    label="Legislação"
    required
  ></v-checkbox>

  <v-checkbox
    v-model="timecheckbox"
    :rules="[v => !!v || 'You must agree to continue!']"
    label="Gestão de Tempo"
    required
  ></v-checkbox>

  <v-checkbox
    v-model="salarycheckbox"
    :rules="[v => !!v || 'You must agree to continue!']"
    label="Salários"
    required
  ></v-checkbox>

  <v-btn
    :disabled="!valid"
    color="success"
    @click="validate">
    Concluir registo
  </v-btn>

</v-form>
